H0.text: Which Australian Prime Minister went for a swim in 1967, never to be seen again. Robert Menzies

H1.text: Which Australian Prime Minister went for a swim in 1967, never to be seen again. John McEwen

H2.text: Which Australian Prime Minister went for a swim in 1967, never to be seen again. John Gorton

H3.text: Which Australian Prime Minister went for a swim in 1967, never to be seen again. Harold Holt

A4.text: Harold Holt disappeared while swimming in rough conditions at Cheviot Beach, Victoria. He was presumed dead, although his body was never recovered
